reviewText: I had this on VHS, wish I had a digital version so I could still watch it.
This  video is a real time capsule. Still funny and warm
My parents had an old copy of this and I watched while growing up.  Finally got myself a copy and I still love it.

I bought this video because my 23 year old son still does a few of the clips from the video and does it well. The last time he saw this video - he was 10 years old and he remembers parts of it like it was yesterday. I think it is a great comedy video for it's time and it is "good clean fun"... It will make you laugh and it has a special energy to it, great improv by Paula. It will always be in my video library.
